{"id":"dee4a908-166f-45e3-9ef6-72493200d4d3","atom_type":"ui_navigation_tactic","funnel_stage":"first_action","observation":"Airtable Omni AI chat: after the AI proposes a plan (e.g. \"Retail Sales CRM\"), the correct action is TYPE in the \"Ask or build anything...\" chat input (e.g. \"Build this\" or \"Yes, create it\"). Clicking \"See details\" only expands the plan card — it does NOT build anything. Clicking the input box without typing is a wasted step. Scroll down past the plan card if no input is visible. Do not click the same \"See details\" element more than once.","result_ref":{"run_id":"20260520_171255","step":21,"screenshot_path":null},"applies_to":{"funnel_stage":["first_action"],"product_category":["Airtable","AI builder"]},"confidence":"confirmed","created_at":"2026-05-21T00:25:56.247658+00:00","last_used_at":null}
